            <lg xml:id="TK1044">
<l>iṟpiṟantār kaṇṇēyu miṉmai yiḷivanta</l>
<l>colpiṟakkuñ cōrvu tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even in those of high birth, poverty will produce the fault of uttering mean words.</l>
